| volume = 131
| pages = 15–31
| last2 = Song
| first2 = C. Z.
| last3 = Green
| first3 = M
}}</ref>
<ref name="molstation">{{cite web|title=Run-off Transcription|url=http://molecularstation.com/dna/run-off-transcription|publisher=Molecular Station|accessdate=April 16, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140422173019/http://molecularstation.com/dna/run-off-transcription|archivedate=April 22, 2014|df=}}</ref><ref name="Lelandais">{{Cite journal
